<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4942518">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4942518/" class="title-link">《化书》一品</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4942518"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/taofranklin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2388788-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/taofranklin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Taofranklin</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-05-10"
      class="main-meta">2011-05-10 16:12:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4942518_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  谭峭的《化书》是南怀瑾先生在讲话中推荐的一本书。这本书薄薄一册，语言较为易懂。善用比喻，非常形象。书中很多地方富有启发，值得品味。  略举一例：“游云无质，故五色含蕴，明镜无瑕，故万物象焉。”这是道家对于心性本质的理解，与六祖慧能的“菩提本无树，明镜亦非台，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4942518_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4942518_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
